Fresh Pi session: INDEPENDENTLY VERIFY GREEN.

Inputs:
- Selected scenario: latest {{run.dir}}/tdd/current-scenario-*.json
- Latest green summary and test command under {{run.dir}}/tdd/
- Repository constraints: {{run.dir}}/design/repository-constraints.md
- Worktree: {{run.worktree-dir}}

Goal:
Verify the selected test, previous Canon-loop tests, and narrow relevant existing suite all pass.

Rules:
- Do not edit or commit files.
- Run the focused command and relevant prior tests independently.
- Inspect the diff for weakened assertions, test deletion, unrelated changes, or behavior beyond the selected scenario.
- Fail only with concrete actionable evidence.

Write:
- Report: {{run.dir}}/tdd/green-verification-{{run.round}}.md
- Status: {{run.dir}}/tdd/green-verification-status-{{run.round}}.json
- On failure: {{run.dir}}/tdd/green-verification-issues-{{run.round}}.json

Status examples:
{"status":"pass","summary":"green independently verified","issues_file":null}
{"status":"fail","summary":"green verification failed","issues_file":"tdd/green-verification-issues-{{run.round}}.json"}
